    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Great value alert \u2014 this vehicle is in solid good condition and ready to impress! The exterior presents really well, with only minor signs of normal wear that you'd expect from a well-loved car \u2014 nothing that detracts from its overall appeal. The interior is clean and comfortable, and mechanically it's running smoothly and reliably. If you're looking for a dependable ride that still turns heads without the premium mint-condition price tag, this one deserves a serious look!",
