    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Here's a wonderful opportunity to own a dependable, well-maintained vehicle at a great price! This car is in good condition \u2014 it runs smoothly, handles confidently, and has clearly been looked after over the years. You'll find the interior is clean and comfortable, and the exterior presents nicely with only minor signs of everyday use. If you're looking for a reliable ride that offers solid value, this one is well worth a look!",
      "price": 33500.0,
