    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\udcb0 $6,000 - A budget-friendly opportunity for the right buyer! \ud83d\udd27 This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 it's a well-worn car that will need some repairs and TLC to get back to its best. The exterior shows noticeable wear, including scratches and dents, and the interior reflects years of use. Mechanically, it will require attention before it's running at full reliability. That said, if you're a hands-on buyer, a DIY enthusiast, or just need affordable transportation with some work involved, this could be your next project! Priced to reflect its current state \u2014 what you see is what you get, and there's real potential here for someone willing to put in the effort. Come take a look! \ud83d\ude97",
      "price": 6000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in truly mint condition \u2014 an exceptional find on the used market that rivals a brand-new purchase in nearly every way. The exterior is pristine, free of any scratches, dents, chips, or paint blemishes, presenting a flawless finish that turns heads. The interior is equally immaculate, with no wear on the seats, carpets, or trim pieces \u2014 everything looks and feels factory fresh. Under the hood, the engine runs with smooth, confident power, and all mechanical systems are in perfect working order with no issues to report. All electronics, features, and accessories function exactly as intended. This is a rare opportunity to own a used vehicle that truly feels new \u2014 ideal for the discerning buyer who refuses to compromise on quality.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture of what you're purchasing. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains a reasonable shine and the body panels are in good shape, though you'll notice some minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with normal use over time. There are no significant dents or rust concerns. The interior is clean and functional, showing moderate wear on the seating surfaces and some light scuffing on high-contact areas like the door panels and center console \u2014 nothing unexpected for a vehicle of this age and use. Mechanically, the car runs reliably and has been maintained adequately; it starts well, drives smoothly, and all major systems are in working order. This is a solid, dependable vehicle that will serve a buyer well in everyday use, but it is not a showroom-quality example. Priced fairly to reflect its honest condition.",
      "price": 35000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition \u2014 a designation that reflects a car that has been well cared for and is ready for reliable daily use. The exterior presents nicely, with paint that retains a healthy shine and only minor surface blemishes consistent with normal use; there are no significant dents, deep scratches, or rust concerns. The interior is clean and comfortable, with upholstery that shows modest wear in high-contact areas but nothing that detracts from the overall experience. All major mechanical systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and suspension \u2014 are functioning properly, and the car drives smoothly and confidently. You can expect a vehicle that doesn't require immediate repairs and is genuinely ready to be driven. Some cosmetic imperfections exist, as is honest to acknowledge, but they are minor and do not affect performance or safety. A pre-purchase inspection is always welcome and encouraged \u2014 we're confident this car will hold up to scrutiny.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    }
